1. *Mrtva* žena ležala je na podu. (The dead woman was lying on the floor.)
2. On se ujutro probudio i shvatio da je *mrtv*. (He woke up in the morning and realized he was dead.)
3. Grad je bio potpuno *mrtv*. (The city was totally dead.)
4. *Mrtvo* drvo nije moglo da raste. (The dead tree couldn't grow.)
5. On je držao *mrtvu* ribu u svojim rukama. (He held a dead fish in his hands.)